{"tid":968435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11月本地零售遜預期 奢侈品轉跌 整體按年僅升1.4% 業界料12月不樂觀","createTime":"2019-01-04T08:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T08:37:02.000Z","uid":229553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b1b2488f510e5e7b040c7e0f5b3e64a9e87e669","tid":968435,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"等睇廣東道無曬珠寶店<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港零售寒風愈趨凜冽，過去支撐市道的珠寶鐘表等貴價貨品增長「神話」不再，2018年初至年底由升轉跌。統計處公布2018年11月零售數據，整體零售總貨值升幅放緩至1.4%，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中珠寶首飾、鐘表及名貴禮物分類「重創」</span>，下跌3.9%，中斷16個月的升浪之餘，更是2017年1月以來最差表現（圖1）。金飾珠寶業界表示，今年以來促銷優惠「未停過」，不過中美貿易戰影響香港經濟，加上人民幣貶值，打擊內地客消費意欲，而高鐵及港珠澳大橋落成，只是加速內地遊客消費模式改變，未能帶動高檔消費。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20190104/s00004/1546540191601/11%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E9%81%9C%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E5%A5%A2%E4%BE%88%E5%93%81%E8%BD%89%E8%B7%8C-%E6%95%B4%E9%AB%94%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%83%85%E5%8D%871-4-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%96%9912%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190104%2Fs00004%2F1546540191601%2F11%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259B%25B6%25E5%2594%25AE%25E9%2581%259C%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%259C%259F-%25E5%25A5%25A2%25E4%25BE%2588%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25BD%2589%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E6%2595%25B4%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%258C%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2583%2585%25E5%258D%25871-4-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2596%259912%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A7%2580&d=tHpTv%2Byl%2BAvHyGucOEPNILZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=37f312f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190104%2Fs00004%2F1546540191601%2F11%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259